NPCName "Abraham"
Location "GAI - Level 4 (4?)"
Description "Abraham is an AI, built to oversee the facility's systems as well as provide complex data analysis and predict probabilities based on these data.\n\nSpecial note: There is one opportunity to ask abraham what he thinks the PC is. This will lead to the pet name 'bloodsack'. If PC picks this option, substitute 'bloodsack' for any other name Abraham gives PC (ie primate)"
Unknown_Desc "You see a old console. It looks like it hasn't been touched in a long time. VITTU \"\" HOMO"
Known_Desc "You see Abraham."
Detailed_Desc "A sleek-looking computer console. A stamp above the concave monitor reads 'Xion 0.9'"
